profile: Powell Tree Services has been proudly serving the communities of Toronto and her surrounding areas for over 30 years. We have always sought to bring a level of professionalism and customer focus to our job while preserving the basic fundamentals of tree and plant care. We have endeavoured to provide a well-rounded set of services so that we can be our clients ‘one-stop-shop’ for all of their tree and plant related needs including tree cutting and removal, stump removal, shrub removal, tree pruning, shrub pruning, cabling & bracing and fertilizing & spraying. We are also available 24 hours for storm-related tree emergencies.
